  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Tower Defense!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/51c8c56ec91e0c4c9b6e384145e02478.avif?t=1772361167\" width=600 height=220 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Goblin Assault is an epic tower defense adventure where you stand against relentless hordes of goblins, monsters, and powerful bosses. Forge your strategy and prepare for a legendary fight!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/2b572a33639ab65d4ef0bb8c38e79e50.webp?t=1772361167\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.poster.avif?t=1772361167\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.webm?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301160/extras/40cf5a0d9927e6ae13570076744a1a08.mp4?t=1772361167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Goblin Assault</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goblin Assault is an epic tower defense game where you defend against waves of goblins, fierce creatures, and mighty bosses determined to crush your defenses. Command a powerful lineup of allied units, unleash devastating spells, and upgrade your towers to hold the line. Each wave brings new challenges, demanding quick thinking and sharp strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span cl